data.description: THIS IS THE ONE YOU HAVE BEEN WAITING FOR! GORGEOUS BRICK 5 bedroom and 4 full bath home on almost an ACRE LOT w/ a finished basement.  Master on Main! SCREENED IN PORCH. BRICK MASONRY outdoor fireplace and huge deck are perfect for entertaining. BIG flat front yard (great for playing ball).  Wooded private backyard. THIS HOME really has it all. Hardwood floors, Open Kitchen to TWO Story Family room w/ fireplace.  Walk in closets. Secondary bedroom on the main floor (could be used for an office) w/ huge palladium window.  Finished "man cave" basement w/ full bath and great unfinished space as well for a workshop, storage or finish it out and make into a theatre room.  Breakfast room overlooking private backyard.  Drink your coffee on the amazing screened in porch. 3 bedrooms upstairs.  RUN don't walk to this meticulously maintained home. Highest and Best due by Saturday 12/12 at 5pm.
